snippet.description:
#TamadaMedia #Wirally
Software Employees and their struggles with their managers.. It's a never ending saga! Pressure cooker is the story of an IT employee Manasa and the pressure she faces in her office with her sinister manager.

Cast: Jaiyetri Makana, Chaitanya Varma, Vamsi krishna lingala, Prakash Jai, Sunandini, Vasanthi,
Kanuri Lakshmikantamani, Annam Krishna Karthik.Manneru Saiteja, Sesh Karthikeya,Pranitha Tejaswini.
Directed By: Vamsi Krishna Lingala
Produced by: Saideep Reddy Borra, Rahul Tamada.
Executive Producer: Anil Kumar Prattipati

Song Lyrics In Hindi

मीठी मीठी बोलै बांगरो आंखां मै तेरे जहर भरा
ती खीती खी तकै ना गणी मरजा णी तनै मा र गरा
देशी जूती पैंट ला जो सूट गजब का या र करा
द्होद्होरै आया हा मी भर दे फेर यो हो या हरा -भरा
फेर बा तां तै  ल छो लै बां गरो
मीठी -मीठी बो लै बां गरो  मीठी मीठी बोलै बांगरो
तू  लया ,सुख अपणा हो या
सा ची रै मेरा सपना हो या
कॉ लम I बणया तू मेरी थो ङी -थो ङी मेरे  ल की मखणा हो या
फेर ला    चखणा हो या तू भर-भर जो  तो लै बां गरो 
ठी -मी ठी बो लै बां गरो  मीठी मीठी बो लै बां गरो 
या ली बणकै घर मै आईए
पेजी गेयां ला ड लडा ईए
मेरी हो का गेयां सजै रै बैठैक ,भाज - भाज तू आग बणाईए
फेर मां मेरी न ममी - ममी बो लै बां गरो
मीठी मीठी बोलै बां गरो  मीठी मीठी बो लै बां गरो

Song Lyrics In English 

mithi mithi bole bangro aankhaan mai tere jaher bharaya
teekhi - teekhi takai nagani marajani tanai maar garya
 desi jooti paint  palazo  suit  gajab ka tyaar kara
 Dhorai aajya hami bharde pher sab kuchh hojya hara -bhara 
 pher bataan tai  ya dil chholai baangaro

 mithi mithi bole bangro aankhaan mai tere jaher bharaya

 tu miljya ,sukh apna ho jya 
 sachee rai mera sapna hojya 
  banaya tu meri thodi thodi  mere dil ki makhna hojya 
 Chakhna hojya mitha laadu tole bangro
 
mithi mithi bole bangro aankhaan mai tere jaher bharaya

 banke byali ghar mai aayiye
 pejee gelta laad ladaiye
 hoke gelya sajai rai baithaik ,bhaj bhajke tu aag banaiye
 pher maa  meri ne mummy mummy bole bangro  
 
mithi mithi bole bangro aankhaan mai tere jaher bharaya

Mann Mast Malang Episode 27 Teaser - 19th April 2025 - HAR PAL GEO

Mann Mast Malang is a love story that traces the journey of two families who, once close and united by their children's engagement, become sworn enemies due to a single incident. As the story unfolds, Kabeer and Riya, former fiancés turned enemies, start to grow closer and eventually fall in love. Their love story faces the challenge of uniting their feuding families, as they strive to make their love successful against all odds.

Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Director: Ali Faizan
Writer: Nooran Makhdoom

snippet.description:

एकदम जब्बर सुपरहिट करायचं...

#SongOutNow

२५ एप्रिल पासून, ‘झापुक झुपूक’ तुमच्या जवळच्या चित्रपटगृहात! 🎬🔥

“Zapuk Zupuk –
Coming to your nearest theatres from 25th April! 🎬🔥

Directed by: Kedar Shinde

Produced by:
Jyoti Deshpande
JioStudiosmarathi 
Jio Studios & Bela Shinde 

प्रमुख भूमिका: Suraj Chavan

Composers : Chandan Kamble 
Singers : Chandan Kamble, Dnyaneshwari Kamble 
Lyrics: Chandan Kamble 
Track Mixed & Mastered by Ajinkya Dhapare @TheSonicStation Mumbai.  
Assistant to Ajinkya - Virat Bhushetty
Music Arrangment: Abhishek Kamble, Omkar Kamble, 
Shainai, Clarnet: Durgesh Bhosle 
Benjo: Sonu Ajmeri 
Recorded By: Tushar Pandit, Prasad Kamble, Shreyash Dandekar 
Music programming: Sudesh Gayakwad 
Rhythm and Percussion: Sachin Bhangre, Nitin Shinde, Nagesh Bhosekar, Arjun Shinde, Krushna Awghade, Lakshman Kamble 
Dholki: Nitin Shinde, Nagesh Bhosekar, Arjun Shinde, Krushna Awghade
Chorus: Prasad Kamble , Ajay Kshirsagar, Omkar Kamble, Pandurang Suryawanshi, Swanand Kamble, Karan Gayakwad, Shivani Kadam, Payal Warungase, Pratiksha Chandane, Samruddhi Rajeshirke, Aishwarya Rajeshirke, Dnyaneshwari Kamble, Vaishnavi Adode
Chorus recording: Dawn Studio 
Rhythm recording: Dawn Studio 
Additional Vocals: Swarchandan Recording Studio Aalandi 
Music recording: Pancham Studio 
Vocal recording: Dawn Studio
Music programming: Sudesh Gayakwad 
Rhythm and Percussion : Sachin Bhangre
Choreographer: Chetan Mahajan, Chetan Shigwan
Co - Choreographer: Rahul Gaikwad , Rushikesh Mestri, Purva Salekar

Cast:
Jui Bhagwat, Indraneil Kamat, Hemant Pharande, Pushkaraj Chirputkar, Mlind Gawali, Deepali Pansare, Payal Jadhav, Swarangi Patil, Sesha Hindlekar, Vihaan Shedge, Bankar Praful, Krupa Gaikwad, Kanha Tiwari

HOD: 
Cinematographer: Udaysingh Mohite
Writer: Omkar Mangesh Datt
Dialogues: Rushikesh Turai
Executive Producer: Ratnakant Jagtap
Makeup: Vishal Vijayrao Shinde
Costume Designer: Yugesha Omkar
Art Director: Nilesh Choudhary
Action Director: Raj Shinde
Sound Designer: Mandar Kamlapurkar
Production Controller: Mitali Rajadhyaksha
Stills & Making: Akshay Lande
Artist Mentor: Abhishek Karangutkar

Lyrics:
रूप गोर लाडाची पोर 
तिला हळद लागली 
हे हळद लागली 
तिला हळद लागली 

हळद गडद पिवळी डोईला बाशिंग बांधून मंडवळी
लाजिरी गोजिरी साजिरी जणू ती दिसती कवळी कर्दळी 
हळदीन नवरी झाली पिवळी पाक 
मग वाजीव दाद्या ढाक नांग टाक नांग ढाक नांग टाक नांग टाक
आर वाजीव दाद्या ढाक नांग टाक नांग ढाक नांग टाक नांग टाक   !!धृ!!

लय धिंगाणा जोरात पोरीन पोरात 
नाचाय आला जोर 
सारी होऊन तराट झिंगुण धुराट
खंगरी चढली तार 
घुमव असकी लाऊन कस  उडव त्यांची झाक
आर वाजीव दाद्या ढाक नांग टाक नांग ढाक नांग टाक नांग टाक
आर वाजीव दाद्या ढाक नांग टाक नांग ढाक नांग टाक नांग टाक
 !!1 !!

ऐ राजा…

लाडाचा मैतर माझा धर र त्याला धर 
लाव हळद तोंडावर अन भरव त्याला पूर 
हलगीच्या ठेक्यावर आंग कापतया थरथर 
मला एंजॉय करुदे त्याला घेऊन खांद्यावर 
घुमक वाल्याला कुणी मारा कीग हाक
आर वाजीव दाद्या वाजीव वाजीव वाजीव 
वाजीव दादा …
आर वाजीव दाद्या ढाक नांग टाक नांग ढाक नांग टाक नांग टाक
आर वाजीव दाद्या ढाक नांग टाक नांग ढाक नांग टाक नांग टाक
!!२!!

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

---------

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. snippet.title: Pahalgam Terror Attack के वीडियो में चश्मदीदों ने रोते-रोते मांगी मदद, क्या बोले? Kashmir Attack
snippet.description:
Gunmen opened fire at a group of tourists in Jammu and Kashmir's Pahalgam. A woman, who was an eyewitness to the attack, narrated the sequence of events as a gunman targeted her husband. The attack took place at around 2:30 pm on Tuesday afternoon when a group of terrorists, dressed in fatigues, opened fire on tourists in Pahalgam's Baisaran meadow. The person who died has been identified as Manjunath and is from Karnataka's Shivamogga.

The copyright ownership in the video rests with India Today Group. No third party is permitted to use the video without obtaining the permission of India Today Group. Any permission for usage can be obtained through the email ID provided here mail@lallantop.com.

snippet.title: नींबू-पुदीना शरबत-चिलचिलाती गर्मी में शरीर को ठंडक दे-आज बनायें-6 महीने तक पियें-Lemon Mint Sharbat
snippet.description:
ताज़गी से भरा ठंडा-पुदीने और नींबू का परफेक्ट कॉम्बो, दादी का नुस्खा, जो आज भी कोल्ड‌ ड्रिंक्स का राजा है, No Color, No essence, no additive, Refreshing Lemon Mint Sharbat
#sharbat  #mojito #colddrink 

Ingredients for Pudina-Lemon Shorbet 
पुदीना - Mint leaves - 3 cup (70g)
नींबू - Lemon - ½ cup
चीनी - Sugar - 4 cup (1 KG)
सौंफ - Fennel - 1 tbsp
अदरक - Ginger - 1 no. (1.5 inch)
काला नमक - Black salt - 1 tbsp

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: भूतनी ने निकाला तांत्रिक के पीछे से बड़ा तरबूज 😆 Sanjay Mishra Comedy Scene - Great Grand Masti
snippet.description:
"Get ready to laugh till your sides hurt with the hilariously naughty antics of three friends in 'Great Grand Masti' (2016)! Join us for a comedy rollercoaster ride full of non-stop entertainment, outrageous situations, and lots of adult humor. Warning: Kindly keep your laughter under control to avoid attracting unwanted attention!"

"तैयार हो जाओ हंसी के लिए 'ग्रेट ग्रैंड मस्ती' (2016) के मजेदार शरारतें के साथ! हमारे साथ एक कॉमेडी रोलरकोस्टर यात्रा पर शामिल हों, जिसमें बिंदास मौज-मस्ती, अविश्वसनीय परिस्थितियां और अश्लील हास्य होता है। चेतावनी: बिना ज्यादा ध्यान दिए हंसी को अधिक न उठाएं!"

Also, Watch Grand Masti Popular Comedy Scenes Here:-

►  मेरी बीवी BMW निकली... "Bewafaa Meri Wife" - https://youtu.be/CqkgUUy4IjU

► अबे तेरा पिछवाड़ा है या विजयवाड़ा? - https://youtu.be/1zO8pESxobk

► OMG मेरी बीवी का चक्कर बॉस के साथ 😂 - https://youtu.be/NgqCd8F8XVY

► हेडमास्टर की बीवी, बेटी और बहन के साथ रंगरलियां मानते पकडे गए ये 3 Idiots - https://youtu.be/_eCsKnPSR5w

► अरे कौआ राजा वहाँ पे चोंच मत मारना, मैं अभी तक बाप भी नहीं बना हूँ - https://youtu.be/DIM8OgjoErU

► पलंग तोड़ सूप पिके तीनो लड़कियाँ हुई Naughty - https://youtu.be/d3mjFs2zbbI

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. snippet.title: 1st Guest At Yuvraj Singh’s 1st Restaurant | Yuvi's Mom Reveals Untold Stories | Sunday Brunch E172
snippet.description:
Join this channel to get access to Uncut & Behind The Scene Videos of your Favourite Celebs:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCDnq05Q89oYq-Tz5boL73Tw/join

I was the first guest at Yuvraj Singh’s first-ever restaurant, Koca, in Gurugram — and it wasn’t just about delicious food. This episode is packed with heartwarming, inspiring, and unheard stories straight from Yuvraj’s life.

I sat down for an intimate conversation with Yuvraj Singh and his mother, Shabnam Singh, where she opened up like never before. From adorable childhood memories of Yuvi, his rebellious streak, and the challenges of raising a champion, to their family’s struggle during his battle with cancer — she shared it all.

We also spoke about Yuvraj’s journey to cricket stardom, his equation with his father Yograj Singh, her parenting style as a single mother, and for the first time, how she was introduced to her daughter-in-law Hazel Keech. It’s a candid, emotional and joyful episode you don’t want to miss!

And of course, you’ll get an exclusive tour of Koca, where Yuvi takes me through his favorite dishes and the story behind launching his dream restaurant.

From the secret behind her legendary Kadhi Chawal, to Yuvraj’s most emotional cricket moments, his battle with cancer, love life with Hazel Keech and becoming a dad at 40, nothing is off the table!


Hit play, join us for this special brunch, and don’t forget to like, comment, and subscribe!

snippet.title: Simran's Fire Speech on Stage 🔥💯 | "I Do Not Deserve This" 😡 - Simran | JFW Movie Awards 2025
snippet.description:
Simran has completed 30 years of being an actress in the industry and has gained respect and love from all over the world! At the JFW Movie Awards 2025, a grand celebration took place as Simran was honoured by more than 10 actresses such as Keerthy Suresh, Krithi Shetty, Parvathy Thiruvothu, Amala Paul, Sri Gouri Priya, Sriya Reddy, Nikhila VImal, Grace Antony, Swasika and Dushara! Simran's speech was bold as she talks about how she received an unnecessary text from a co-star and that she rather do "Aunty" roles than roles that do not mean anything! 

Simran recently did a cameo in the blockbuster hit "Good Bad Ugly" and was praised for her brilliant performance and her iconic dance was used in the movie with Ajith Kumar!

Watch the video now and let us know your feedback in the comments section below!

snippet.title: Gurugram: स्कॉर्पियो सवार बदमाशों ने बाइकर्स ग्रुप को पीटा, AI की मदद से आरोपियों का ऐसे पता चला?
snippet.description:
गुरुग्राम में बाइक राइडर्स के एक ग्रुप पर हमले की घटना सामने आई है. जानकारी के मुताबिक, बाइक राइडर्स सुबह ब्रेकफास्ट करने निकले थे. इस दौरान स्कार्पियों में सवार कुछ लोगों से उनकी बहस हो गई. जिसके बाद आरोपियों ने राइडर्स से मारपीट की और उनकी बाइक को क्षति पहुंचाई. पुलिस ने आरोपियों की पहचान कर ली है.

A shocking road rage incident unfolded on Gurugram’s Dwarka Expressway, where some men brutally attacked a group of bikers with baseball bats, captured on camera. On April 20, 2025, one biker, Hardik Sharma, was injured, and his ₹11 lakh superbike was damaged. The attackers, reportedly bodybuilders from Delhi, were allegedly intoxicated. The police have registered a case and begun investigations. In this video, we dive into the causes of this incident, the growing issue of road rage, and ways to stay safe.

The copyright ownership in the video rests with India Today Group. No third party is permitted to use the video without obtaining the permission of India Today Group. Any permission for usage can be obtained through the email ID provided here mail@lallantop.com.

इस वीडियो का कॉपीराइट स्वामित्व इंडिया टुडे ग्रुप के पास है. इंडिया टुडे ग्रुप की अनुमति के बिना, किसी तीसरे पक्ष को वीडियो का उपयोग करने की आज्ञा नहीं है. उपयोग की अनुमति इस ईमेल आईडी mail@lallantop.com के माध्यम से प्राप्त की जा सकती है.
